                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8084" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1257</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4159 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川长虹：搭建数智化供应链融资平台 共筑政企“长”远合作彩“虹”桥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Government-enterprise Cooperation in Establishing A Digitalized Supply Chain Financing Platform —— a Case Analysis Based On Sichuan Changhong</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙莹，刘琦，宋云吉，王璐</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国海洋大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川长虹</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川长虹；供应链金融；应收账款融资；产融政企合作</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sichuan Changhong; Supply Chain Finance; Accounts Receivable Financing; Government-enterprise Cooperation in Production and Finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了四川长虹在与绵阳政府、人民银行的通力协作下，以产融政企合作为原则，以互联网大数据为技术支撑，构建起数智化应收账款融资平台的动因、过程和效果，并细致分析和归纳其具体的运作方式、模式机理与特色。为了缓解供应链上下游企业融资困境、弥补传统保理业务不足，四川长虹首创应收账款融资长虹模式，依托供应链中核心企业的信用，将中小企业持有的零散的、难以确权的应收账款融资资源，通过供应链金融平台进行单笔拆分、多笔合并，最终实现迅速流转变现。整个模式在操作流程、风险控制方面独具特色，促进了中小供应商的良性发展，实现了政府、企业、金融机构等多方的合作共赢，为其他企业创新供应链融资模式提供有益参考。本案例旨在通过案例的解读与分析，引导学生掌握应收账款融资长虹模式的机制与应用要点，提高创新供应链融资新模式的能力，从而实现知识层面、能力层面和价值层面的综合提升。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes Sichuan Changhong, a leading household appliance manufacturer, in collaboration with Mianyang government and People&#39;s Bank of China, on the principle of cooperation between industry, finance and government, supported by Internet big data and based on information sharing and credit transfer, and analyzes and summarizes its operation mode and mode mechanism. In order to alleviate the financing difficulties of upstream and downstream enterprises in the supply chain, Sichuan Changhong pioneered the Changhong model of accounts receivable financing, which is based on the credit of core enterprises in the supply chain and realized the accounts receivable held by small and medium-sized enterprises through the supply chain financial platform. The whole model has its own characteristics in operation process and risk control, which has promoted the benign development of small and medium-sized enterprises, achieved win-win cooperation among the government, enterprises and financial institutions, and provided useful reference for other enterprises to innovate the supply chain financing model.This case aims to guide students to master the mechanism and application points of the Changhong model of accounts receivable financing through case interpretation and analysis, improve their ability to innovate new supply chain financing models, and achieve comprehensive improvement in knowledge, ability and value.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《内部控制与风险管理》、《大数据与财务决策》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链金融；应收账款融资；风险控制理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
